    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>In this cohort of 42 patients with mild COVID19 we found a unique clinical feature of acute anosmia and dysgeusia in more than third of patients. Median onset of these features was 3.3 days after onset of illness (range 0-7) with rapid recovery in most patients.</jats:p>\n                <jats:sec>\n                  <jats:title>Article Summary Line</jats:title>\n                  <jats:p>Anosmia and dysgeusia appeared early in third of our patients with mild SARS-CoV-2 infection and were short-lived in most patients.</jats:p>\n                </jats:sec>",
